<head>WIDOW</head><list type="translations"><item xml:lang="zh">寡婦</item></list>
<div type="definition">
<p>WIFE BEREAVED of her HUSBAND OR WOMAN LACKING a HUSBAND.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="huang-jingui">
<p>HUANG JINGUI 2006</p>
<p>HUMAN AFFAIRS 29. UNMARRIED LADY</p>
<p>寡，老而無夫的婦人或有夫獨守的婦人。</p>
<p>孀，喪夫之婦，方言詞。</p>
<p>嫠，喪夫之婦。</p>
<p>怨女，超過婚齡而無夫的女性。</p>
<p>巫兒，留家不嫁的長女。</p></div>
